API Endpoints Summary
1. Authentication APIs (4)
POST /api/auth/register

POST /api/auth/login

POST /api/auth/logout

GET /api/auth/me

2. Player APIs (3)
GET /api/player/:id

PUT /api/player/:id

DELETE /api/player/:id (admin only)

3. Game Session APIs (4)
POST /api/game/start

GET /api/game/session/:id

POST /api/game/session/:id/step

POST /api/game/session/:id/end

4. Product & Instruction APIs (3)
GET /api/products

GET /api/products/:id

GET /api/instructions/:difficulty

5. Leaderboard APIs (3)
GET /api/leaderboard

POST /api/leaderboard

GET /api/leaderboard/player/:id

6. Admin APIs (3)
GET /api/admin/players

GET /api/admin/attempts

GET /api/admin/leaderboard (download)

7. Assets & Analytics APIs (3)
GET /api/assets/icons

GET /api/assets/fonts

POST /api/analytics/event

8. Realtime (Optional)
WebSocket endpoint: /api/game/realtime

